      "content": "but i havent even seen that brand in a store or an ad on my phone. i dont even drink soda. it's like it's just being beamed into my head when i sleep. it feels so intentional, like they're trying to get the name stuck in my brain. how is that just a coincidence? it feels way more sinister than just stress.",
